    {
      "response_id": "personal_logger_1",
      "text": "Been swinging an axe since I could lift one. The forest provides, if you're willing to work for it.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["hardworking", "practical"],
      "min_disposition": 30,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["elder_moor"],
      "weight": 1.2,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_logger_2",
      "text": "Tharin's a fair boss, for a dwarf. Pays on time, doesn't work us to death. Could be worse.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["practical", "content"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["elder_moor"],
      "weight": 1.1,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_logger_3",
      "text": "I was born right here in Elder Moor, you know. First generation. Watched this camp become a proper hamlet.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["proud", "nostalgic"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["elder_moor"],
      "weight": 1.1,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_logger_4",
      "text": "The work's hard, but honest. Better than farming swamp mud or begging in Dalhurst. Got my pride, at least.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["proud", "hardworking"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["elder_moor"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_logger_5",
      "text": "Lost two fingers to a saw three winters back. *holds up hand* Still swing an axe better than most with all ten.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["tough", "proud"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["elder_moor"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_logger_6",
      "text": "My father came here when the camp was first established. I was born in that very cabin. Never been anywhere else.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["traditional", "content"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["elder_moor"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_logger_wolves",
      "text": "Had to fight off a wolf last week. Big bastard, almost got my throat. This place is getting more dangerous every year.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["tough", "worried"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["elder_moor"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_farmer_1",
      "text": "I'm just a simple farmer, working the land like my father before me. It's not glamorous, but it's honest work.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["humble", "traditional"],
      "min_disposition": 30,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["farmer"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_farmer_2",
      "text": "The crops are doing well this season, thank the gods. Last year's drought nearly ruined us.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["humble", "optimistic"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["farmer"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_farmer_3",
      "text": "I work the fields from dawn to dusk. Honest work for honest pay. Can't ask for more than that.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["humble", "hardworking"],
      "min_disposition": 30,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["farmer"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_farmer_wolves",
      "text": "Lost half my flock to wolves last winter. Been rebuilding ever since. The moors are getting more dangerous.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["weary", "concerned"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["farmer"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_guard_1",
      "text": "I serve to protect these people. It's not always glorious, but someone has to stand between them and the darkness.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["dutiful", "noble"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["guard"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_guard_2",
      "text": "Night watch is the worst. You see things moving in the dark. Hear sounds that shouldn't be. Makes you question what's real.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["nervous", "observant"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["guard"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_guard_3",
      "text": "Twenty years I've stood at this post, through rain, snow, and worse. Seen a lot of things come and go.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["veteran", "stoic"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["guard"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_guard_4",
      "text": "The pay's not much, but there's nobility in protecting folk who can't protect themselves.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["humble", "dutiful"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["guard"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_merchant_1",
      "text": "Trade's been slow lately. Folk are hoarding their coin, worried about what's coming. Can't say I blame them.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["pragmatic", "worried"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["merchant"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_merchant_2",
      "text": "I traveled here from the eastern kingdoms. The roads were dangerous, but the opportunities here were worth the risk.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["adventurous", "ambitious"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["merchant"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_merchant_3",
      "text": "Coin makes the world turn, friend. Learn that lesson early and you'll go far. Everything else is just sentiment.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["cynical", "pragmatic"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["merchant"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_merchant_4",
      "text": "My family's been in the trade for generations. We know the value of a fair deal and a good reputation.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["traditional", "proud"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["merchant"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_innkeeper_1",
      "text": "Been running this inn for fifteen years now. Seen a lot of folk come through those doors. All sorts.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["experienced", "observant"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["innkeeper"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_innkeeper_2",
      "text": "You meet all sorts in this line of work. Farmers, merchants, adventurers, nobles in disguise. Everyone needs a bed and a meal.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["friendly", "observant"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["innkeeper"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_innkeeper_3",
      "text": "I've got stories that would curl your hair, friend. But those are for after a few drinks, not idle conversation.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["mysterious", "friendly"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["innkeeper"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_blacksmith_1",
      "text": "I've worked this forge since I was old enough to lift a hammer. The heat and the metal, it's in my blood now.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["dedicated", "traditional"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["blacksmith"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_blacksmith_2",
      "text": "Every blade I forge is a piece of myself. I put my heart into my work. Can't do it any other way.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["passionate", "proud"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["blacksmith"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_blacksmith_dwarf",
      "text": "Learned my craft from a dwarf in Kazan-Dun. Spent five years in those mountain forges. Best education I ever had.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["experienced", "respectful"],
      "min_disposition": 45,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["blacksmith"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_chronos_1",
      "text": "I heard Father Time's calling when I was young. The turning of ages, the inevitability of fate. It spoke to me.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "scholarly"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_chronos"],
      "weight": 1.3,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_chronos_2",
      "text": "I measure time. I record history. Every moment that passes, I account for it. That is my purpose.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["meticulous", "dedicated"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_chronos"],
      "weight": 1.2,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_chronos_3",
      "text": "The other priests... the Morthane clergy... they claim the final count. But it is Father Time who measures every grain of sand.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["jealous", "resentful"],
      "min_disposition": 45,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_chronos"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_chronos_4",
      "text": "Time reveals all truths, child. What is hidden will be known. What is done will be remembered. Nothing escapes the count.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["wise", "prophetic"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_chronos"],
      "weight": 1.1,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_chronos_blessing",
      "text": "May Father Time bless you, Child. May your moments be well-measured and your hours well-spent.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "formal"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_chronos"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_gaela_1",
      "text": "Gaela teaches us to nurture and protect. The earth provides, and we must give back. It's a simple truth.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["serene", "nurturing"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_gaela"],
      "weight": 1.3,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_gaela_2",
      "text": "I tend the temple gardens. Watch the seasons turn, the crops grow, the fruit ripen. All in Gaela's time.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["peaceful", "patient"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_gaela"],
      "weight": 1.2,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_gaela_3",
      "text": "The farmers come to me before planting, after harvest. Their faith is simple and pure. Gaela smiles upon them.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["humble", "appreciative"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_gaela"],
      "weight": 1.1,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_gaela_4",
      "text": "All things grow in their season. All things rest when winter comes. There is peace in the cycle, if you accept it.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["serene", "philosophical"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_gaela"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_gaela_blessing",
      "text": "May Gaela's warmth find your fields. May your harvest be plentiful and your winters mild.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "kind"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_gaela"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_morthane_1",
      "text": "Morthane teaches that death is not an ending, but a transformation. The soul passes through the door to what lies beyond.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["morbid", "philosophical"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_morthane"],
      "weight": 1.3,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_morthane_2",
      "text": "People fear us. They see death and think us dark. But we merely guide souls through the threshold. There is comfort in that.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["misunderstood", "patient"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_morthane"],
      "weight": 1.2,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_morthane_3",
      "text": "The undead... they trouble us most of all. Souls trapped in the doorway, unable to pass through. Morthane weeps for them.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["somber", "sad"],
      "min_disposition": 45,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_morthane"],
      "weight": 1.1,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_morthane_4",
      "text": "I perform the funeral rites. Speak the words that ease the passage. It is sacred work, though few appreciate it.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["devoted", "resigned"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_morthane"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_morthane_suspicion",
      "text": "Yes, I've heard the whispers. That we consort with the undead, that we worship the darkness. It is... wearying to be so misunderstood.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["weary", "frustrated"],
      "min_disposition": 50,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_morthane"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_morthane_blessing",
      "text": "May Morthane's door open gently for you. May your transition, when it comes, be peaceful.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "somber"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest_morthane"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_generic_1",
      "text": "I serve the gods with all my heart. It is my purpose, my calling. I could imagine no other life.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["devout", "dedicated"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_priest_generic_2",
      "text": "Even priests have doubts in the dark hours. Faith is not the absence of questions, but the courage to continue despite them.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["honest", "philosophical"],
      "min_disposition": 50,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": ["temple", "priest"],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_civilian_backstory_1",
      "text": "Born and raised right here. This place is in my bones. Couldn't imagine living anywhere else.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["traditional", "content"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_civilian_backstory_2",
      "text": "Fled here during the wars in the east. Lost everything, but at least we have our lives. Starting over is hard.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["weary", "resilient"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_civilian_backstory_3",
      "text": "Came here looking for work. Heard there were opportunities. It's been harder than I expected, but I'm making it.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["determined", "pragmatic"],
      "min_disposition": 35,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_civilian_backstory_4",
      "text": "I followed my husband here when he found work. It wasn't my choice, but home is where your family is.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["accepting", "loyal"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_civilian_dalhurst",
      "text": "Had some trouble back in Dalhurst. Rather not talk about it. Came here for a fresh start, and that's what I got.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["secretive", "guarded"],
      "min_disposition": 45,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_family_1",
      "text": "My children are my whole world. Everything I do, I do for them. They deserve better than I had.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["caring", "dedicated"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_family_2",
      "text": "Lost my mother to the fever three winters back. Still miss her every day. She held this family together.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["grieving", "nostalgic"],
      "min_disposition": 45,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_family_3",
      "text": "My brother went off adventuring years ago. Never came back. I try not to think about what might have happened.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["worried", "sad"],
      "min_disposition": 45,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_family_4",
      "text": "Been married thirty years this spring. Can't imagine life without her. We've weathered a lot together.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["content", "loyal"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },

    {
      "response_id": "personal_dreams_1",
      "text": "I dream of seeing the ocean someday. Never been more than a day's walk from home. They say it goes on forever.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["hopeful", "curious"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_dreams_2",
      "text": "I'm saving up to open my own shop someday. Just a small place, but it would be mine. That's the dream.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["ambitious", "hopeful"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
      "max_disposition": 100,
      "required_knowledge": [],
      "weight": 1.0,
      "actions": [],
      "conditions": []
    },
    {
      "response_id": "personal_dreams_3",
      "text": "When I was young, I wanted to be a knight. Dreamed of armor and glory. Life had other plans for me.",
      "topic_type": 2,
      "personality_affinity": ["wistful", "accepting"],
      "min_disposition": 40,
